<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Lavender Recovery</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background-image: url("https://i.imgur.com/sTtr8a8.jpg");
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-attachment: local;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      max-width: 1920pxpx;
      max-height: 1080px;

    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
    }

    .landing {
      max-height: 1080px;
      max-width: 1920px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .landing-left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-left: 40px;
    }

    .desc {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      color: lavender;
      font-size: 35px;
      background-color: rgba(1, 1, 1, .50);
      margin-left: 150px;
      margin-right: 50px;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    }

    .landing-right {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: -100px;
    }

    .lav-home {
      justify-content: center;
      background: lavender;
      height: 400px;
      width: 400px;
      border-radius: 70%;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 40px;

    }

    .home-text {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 60px;
      font-family: 'Redressed', cursive;
      padding: 40px 50px 50px 50px;


    }


    /* styling for login form */
    .login-form {
      position: relative;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      border: solid;
      border-color: mintcream;
      width: 260px;
      font-family: 'Redressed', cursive;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));
      ;
      margin-left: 55px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;


    }

    .email-input {
      padding: 10px;
      margin-left: 30px;
      border: 1px;
    }

    .auth-email {
      font-size: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      color: aliceblue;
      padding-left: 1px;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }

    .email-div {
      padding-left: 15px;
    }

    .password-input {
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px;
      margin-left: 30px;
    }

    .auth-password {
      font-size: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      color: aliceblue;
      margin-left: -5px;
      padding-left: 5px;
    }

    .pass-div {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .log {
      padding-left: 105px;
      padding-top: 30px;
    }

    .login-button {
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Redressed', cursive;
      color: white;
      background-color: black;
      font-size: 15px;
      border-radius: 70%;
      padding-top: 6px;
      padding-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .sign-up {
      width: 200px;
      text-align: center;
      color: black;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding-right: 30px;
      padding-left: 35px;
      padding-bottom: 25px;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(230, 230, 250, 1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));
      font-size: 25px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-left: 55px;



    }

    .sign-btn {
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Redressed', cursive;
      color: black;
      background-color: lavender;
      font-size: 12px;
      border-radius: 70%;
      padding-top: 6px;
      border: white;
      font-size: 20px;

    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="landing">
    <div class="landing-left">
      <div class="lav-home">
        <p class="home-text">Lavender Recovery</p>
      </div>
      <div class="login-form">
        <form action="/auth" method="POST">
          <div class="email-div">
            <p class="auth-email">Email</p>
            <input class="email-input" id="auth-email" type="email" name="email">
          </div>
          <div class="pass-div">
            <p class="auth-password">Password</p>
            <input class="password-input" id="auth-password" type="password" name="password">
          </div>
          <div class="log">
            <input class="login-button" type="submit" value="login">
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="sign-up">
        <p>Not a member yet?</p>
        <p> Join the Community!</p>
        <a class="sign-btn" href="/auth/signup">Signup</a>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="landing-right">
      <p class="desc">Being sober in the LGBTQI+ community can be challenging when fellowship is often substance-use
        focused.
        Lavender Recovery creates a safe space to share heartache and most importantly, celebrate life.
        We are an empowering, supportive community committed to raising the voices of queer recovering addicts and
        alcoholics.
        Whether you're questioning your sexuality or sobriety, you are welcome here.
        Together, we stand strong in the face of adversity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>






</body>

</html>